&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/LATAM-QUITO-ZAZU-OFFER-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4555&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/LATAM-QUITO-ZAZU-OFFER-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LATAM- QUITO- ZAZU- OFFER- MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;190&quot; height=&quot;58&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
One of Quito&rsquo;s hippest restaurants, the comfortably sleek room is one where guests are able to have a romantic, luxurious dinner featuring Ecuadorian cuisine with Peruvian influence.&nbsp;&nbsp; Service is sophisticated and friendly. Before or after dinner, have a drink at the lively bar. Zazu is a &lt;strong&gt;Relais &amp;amp; Chateaux Restaurant&lt;/strong&gt; and has achieved the &lt;strong&gt;Wine Spectator Magazine 2013 Award of Excellence&lt;/strong&gt;. Attire is chic casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book by contacting Zazu by phone at +593 2 254 3559&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Booking Requirements &ndash;If you wish to take part in the Private Cooking Class Dinner Experience, please mention this to the hostess at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Cooking Class Dinner Experience includes Dinner and paired wines that have been cooked in the class. The price is $70 per person. No minimum number of guests but up to 12 guests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy &ndash; As a courtesy Zazu asks for a 24 hour advance notice for standard reservations and 48 hours if you have booked the Private Cooking Class&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advance booking recommendation &ndash; Zazu recommends booking with 7 day; advance notice for standard reservations and 14 days for Private Cooking Class&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Cooking Class Dinner Experience will be held in Zazu&rsquo;s private second floor test kitchen and will have a duration of approximately 3 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred bookings based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

